<h3><font color="blue">INTRODUCTION</font></h3>
Do you have the grit ,the passion ,and the skills to be an ultimate CHEM-E ,are you the one out there to tell the world i'm better than the rest. At Tathva 13, test your wits against the best of grey cells!<img src="file:///android_asset/chq/quiz_resized.jpg" alt="quiz.jpg"/>
                                    Concorso is a chemical quizzing event that tests the very basics of chemical engineering concepts and its applications at industrial level, the same basics that we sometimes forget when we try to remember the special cases, finer applications and so on in the course of our study. So get ready to unleash your potential to face Concorso!
<h3><font color="blue">INTRODUCTION</font></h3>


<h3><font color="blue">SPECIFICATIONS</font></h3>
<ul>
<li>Questions can be from core chemical engineering topics like Mass transfer, Heat transfer, Fluid mechanics, Process Instrumentation, Process Control, Safety Engineering, Process economics etc. The quiz will test the chemical engineering aptitude of the contestant.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>               A preliminary written round followed by final round for which 6 teams are selected </li>

</ul>

<h3><font color="blue">QUIZ MASTER</font></h3>
The event will be held in association with IIChe and hosted by renowned Quiz master Mr.Harinath of BPCL.

